<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Sigurnost</title>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="author" content="Mihael Cugovčan" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/main.css" />
    <script src="/main.js"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body class="centered">
    <div class="header">
        <h1 style="text-align: center; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Testiranje sigurnosti aplikacije</h1>
        <div>
            <a href="/">
                <button class="button">Početna</button>
            </a>
            <a href="/sqlinjection">
                <button class="button">SQL injection</button>
            </a>
            <a href="/brokenauth">
                <button class="button">Broken authentication</button>
            </a>
            
        </div>
        
    </div>
    <div style="background-color: #e1e1e1;">
        <br />
        <div>Odaberite način rada:</div>
        <input type="radio" id="nes" name="odabrano" value="1" onclick="pokaziSQL(this)" checked>
        <label for="nes">Nesigurno</label><br>
        <input type="radio" id="sig" name="odabrano" value="2" onclick="pokaziSQL(this)">
        <label for="sig">Sigurno</label><br>
        <br />
        <section class="readme-naslov">
            <div>Prvi input je primjer slanja SQL upita koji je sklon SQL injection napadu</div>
            <div>Potrebno je upisati tekst koji je tautologija tipa <b>2 OR 1 = 1</b> i vratit će se sva korisnička imena</div>
            <div>Također je moguće dobiti sve lozinke upisom teksta <b>2 UNION SELECT korisnicko_ime, lozinka FROM korisnik</b></div>
        </section>
        <div id="nesigurno">
        <label for="idinput1">Unesite ID:</label>
        <input type="id" id="idinput1" name="idinput1">
        <button onclick="searchId()">Pretraga</button>
        <br/>
        <div id="iddiv1" style="color: red"></div>
        <br/>
        </div>
        <section class="readme-naslov">
            <div>Drugi input je primjer slanja SQL upita koji je otporan na SQL injection napad</div>
            <div>Provjerava se je li to što je upisano zapravo ID tj. može li se parsirati kao broj</div>
            <div>Dostupni ID-ovi za testiranje: <b>2 i 3</b></div>
        </section>
        <div id="sigurno" style="visibility: hidden">
        <label for="idinput2">Unesite ID:</label>
        <input type="id" id="idinput2" name="idinput2">
        <button onclick="searchIdFixed()">Pretraga</button>
        <br/>
        <div id="iddiv2" style="color: red"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>